nodes.bodyText: Do we need to also intercept AfterAll / AfterEach? And all the other methods :-)

There might will be situations were we have to, but they are unlikely to ever come up with this kind of internal test (hopefully 😆).
I say we leave it as is for now and fix if it ever comes up.
